Given the following record definition:

record Person(String name, int age) {}

Which of the following statements about this record are true? (Choose two)

What is the result of the following code?

var text = """
    Hello
    World
    """;
System.out.println(text.length());

Given the following sealed class hierarchy:

sealed class Shape permits Circle, Rectangle {}
final class Circle extends Shape {}
final class Rectangle extends Shape {}

Which statement is true?

What is the output of the following pattern matching code?

Object obj = "Hello";
if (obj instanceof String s) {
    System.out.println(s.length());
} else {
    System.out.println(s);
}

